To analyze the Swedish sentence "Viruset aktiveras då användaren kör det program som viruset infekterat," we will first identify the heads of each word and measure the dependency distances accordingly. 

1. Viruset (head: aktiveras, distance: 1)
2. aktiveras (head: [root], distance: 0)
3. då (head: aktiveras, distance: 1)
4. användaren (head: kör, distance: 2)
5. kör (head: aktiveras, distance: 2)
6. det (head: program, distance: 2)
7. program (head: kör, distance: 2)
8. som (head: program, distance: 1)
9. viruset (head: infekterat, distance: 1)
10. infekterat (head: [root], distance: 0)

Now we will calculate the total distances:
- Viruset to aktiveras: 1
- aktiveras to itself: 0
- då to aktiveras: 1
- användaren to kör: 2
- kör to aktiveras: 2
- det to program: 2
- program to kör: 2
